\f1 \cf2 \cb4 inc\cb5 \
\cb4 dec
\f0 \cf3 \cb5 \
As you might be able to guess, the inc command increases the data in local storage by one, and dec decreases it by one.\
For better addition and subtraction, use the add and sub commands.\

\f1 \cf6 \cb7 add \cf3 <var>\cf6 \cb5 \
